OL,3,CTreasury denies coppers could be
OL,4,Cscrapped after none ordered by Royal
OL,5,CMint
OL,7,FThe Treasury says it is "confident
OL,8,Fthere are enough coins in the system"
OL,9,Fas it denied 1p and 2p coins would be
OL,10,Fscrapped after none were ordered from
OL,11,Fthe Royal Mint this year.
OL,13,FReports had suggested the coins could
OL,14,Fbe reaching the end of their run amid
OL,15,Fthe continuing decline in cash use.
OL,17,FBut a Treasury spokesman denied it is
OL,18,Fthe end of the road for the coins and
OL,19,Fsaid the lack of orders is down to
OL,20,Fthere being enough already in
OL,21,Fcirculation.
