OL,7,F"We are not scrapping 1p or 2p coins,"
OL,8,Fthey said. "We are confident there are
OL,9,Fenough coins in the system without the
OL,10,Fneed to order more this year."
OL,12,FThe Royal Mint responds to demand
OL,13,Flevels by issuing coins on behalf of
OL,14,Fthe Treasury, which then decides how
OL,15,Fmany new coins are issued into
OL,16,Fcirculation.
OL,18,FNo 1p coins were minted in 2018 or
OL,19,F2019 and no 2p coins were minted in
OL,20,F2018, 2019, 2020 or 2022, according to
OL,21,Ffigures on the Royal Mint's website.
