OL,7,FThere has been speculation in previous
OL,8,Fyears that the Treasury could be
OL,9,Fpaving the way for the end of 1p and
OL,10,F2p coins, after comments were invited
OL,11,Fon the mix of coins in circulation.
OL,13,FBut in 2019, government plans to
OL,14,Fsafeguard the future of cash were set
OL,15,Fout and in 2023 legislation was passed
OL,16,Fas part of the Financial Services and
OL,17,FMarkets Act, to protect access to cash.
